GOING FOR GOLD by #HerreraBeauty

@laracosima_ embodies the essence of holiday glam, with rich textures and luminous hues. On the eyes, #HerreraBeauty’s ultra-blendable Chic Mono Shimmer Eyeshadow in Gold 17 and Smoke 19 create a glittering take on the classic smokey eye, finished here with lengthening Fabulous Eyes Mascara. Good Girl Gloss in Soft Pink 975 for a touch of shine on the lips and Fabulous Skin Highlighter to complete the look.

Shop online for selected countries at carolinaherrera.com.

